commands: jq --arg buildroot "$FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR" --argjson data '{"@electron/node-gyp@git+https://github.com/electron/node-gyp.git#06b29aafb7708acef8b3669835c8a7857ebc92d2": "flatpak-node/git-packages/@electron/node-gyp-06b29aafb7708acef8b3669835c8a7857ebc92d2#06b29aafb7708acef8b3669835c8a7857ebc92d2"}' 'walk(    if type == "object"    then        to_entries | map(            if (.value | type == "string") and $data[.value]            then .value = "git+file:\($buildroot)/\($data[.value])"            else .            end        ) | from_entries    else .    end)' $FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR/package.json > $FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR/package.json.new

jq --arg buildroot "$FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR" --argjson data '{"git+ssh://git@github.com/electron/node-gyp.git#06b29aafb7708acef8b3669835c8a7857ebc92d2": "flatpak-node/git-packages/@electron/node-gyp-06b29aafb7708acef8b3669835c8a7857ebc92d2#06b29aafb7708acef8b3669835c8a7857ebc92d2", "ssh://git@github.com/electron/node-gyp.git#06b29aafb7708acef8b3669835c8a7857ebc92d2": "flatpak-node/git-packages/@electron/node-gyp-06b29aafb7708acef8b3669835c8a7857ebc92d2#06b29aafb7708acef8b3669835c8a7857ebc92d2"}' 'walk(    if type == "object" and (.version | type == "string") and $data[.version]    then        .version = "git+file:\($buildroot)/\($data[.version])"    else .    end)' $FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR/package-lock.json > $FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR/package-lock.json.new
